column5: got out on lake erie tuesday in front of the windmills cought 60 perch kept 30 over 10inch and 10 over 13inch
Congrats to you. Sounds like a feast about to happen.

Lots of perch out of the mouth of the Grand River now also ...just gota have a North Wind and they are getting limits ...if the lake is rough fish the river for Walleye bite was good for us yesterday after getting blown off the lake ...
Good going Corvy Sounds like you got slimed also
